'''2006年跨大西洋航機恐怖襲擊陰謀'''是指一宗[[恐怖主義|恐怖份子]]懷疑會在[[英國|英國]]飛往[[美國|美國]]的航班上發動爆炸的陰謀。<ref>{{cite web|author=Bob Sherwood與Stephen Fidler|title=MI5 tracked group for a year|publisher=《[[金融時報|金融時報]]》|accessdate=2006-08-11|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/cbed2e12-28b5-11db-a2c1-0000779e2340.html|archive-date=2006-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061026170433/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/cbed2e12-28b5-11db-a2c1-0000779e2340.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2006年8月10日，[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]宣佈拘捕本次陰謀的主要涉案人士，全部都是擁有英國國籍的[[穆斯林|伊斯兰教徒]]。當局表示由於有關襲擊計劃「已經接近執行階段」，所以立即干擾这次陰謀。<ref>{{cite web|author=Eric Pfanner|title=Pakistan Says It Played Key Role in Inquiry|publisher=《[[國際先驅論壇報|國際先驅論壇報]]》|accessdate=2006-08-11|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/11/world/europe/11cnd-terror.html?_r=1&oref=slogin|archive-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621224113/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/11/world/europe/11cnd-terror.html?_r=1&oref=slogin|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name ="BBC-statements">{{cite web|author=英國廣播公司新聞|title=Ministers' statements in full|publisher=[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]|accessdate=2006-08-10|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/4778817.stm|archive-date=2017-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170826160904/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/4778817.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNN-SecurityChief">{{cite web|author=CNN.com|title=Security chief: Airline terror plot 'close to execution'|publisher=[[CNN|有線電視新聞網]]|accessdate=2006-08-10|url=http://www.cnn.com/2006/US/08/10/us.security/index.html|archive-date=2010-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100825054344/http://www.cnn.com/2006/US/08/10/us.security/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>據美國情報方面官員稱，涉案人士計劃於拘捕行動後兩天內進行襲擊預演。<ref>{{cite web|author=Lare Jakes Jordan|title=U.S. posts code-red alert; bans liquids|publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|accessdate=2006-08-10|url= http://www.chron.com/disp/story.mpl/ap/politics/4108668.html}}</ref>但是據不知名的保安方面消息指，涉案人士尚未購票，而部分更未持有護照。<ref>Target America, Terror in the sky, [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oPloNEasfUQ （YouTube）] {{Wayback|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oPloNEasfUQ |date=20200229122757 }}，[[全國廣播公司|全國廣播公司]]，2006年8月12日</ref><ref name="msnbc 14320452">http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14320452/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/14320452/ |date=20110215104559 }} [[MSNBC|MSNBC]]，U.S., U.K. at odds over timing of arrests</ref>當局亦在[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]拘捕部分涉案人士。<ref name="arrests in Italy">{{cite web|author=FOXNews.com|title=Pakistan: Suspected London Plane Terrorists Have Al Qaeda Connection|publisher=[[FOX|霍士新聞]]|accessdate=2006-08-11|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,207898,00.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060819042401/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,207898,00.html|archive-date=2006-08-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>警方消息在8月17日向英國廣播公司透露，在[[海威科姆|海威科姆]]的樹林裏發現一個裝有所有可以組裝炸彈材料的公事包，而第二天警方也懷疑在檢獲的手提電腦中，找到被捕疑犯製作的殉道錄影片段。[[倫敦警方|倫敦警方]]尚未對其發現發表正式聲明。<ref name="BBC-bombkit">{{cite web|author=英國廣播公司英國新聞|title=Terror detectives 'find bomb kit'|publisher=[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]|accessdate=2006-08-17|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/5261086.stm|archive-date=2020-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611060244/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/5261086.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

