== 審訊 ==
在英國，最終有8人（Ahmed Abdullah Ali、Assad Sarwar、Tanvir Hussain、Ibrahim Savant、Arafat Khan、Waheed Zaman、Umar Islam、Mohammed Gulzar）因本次恐怖襲擊陰謀被起訴，審訊於2008年4月開始。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7329221.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=2008-04-03 |title='Airliners Plot': The allegations |accessdate=2009-02-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5whI2eO7D?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7329221.stm |archivedate=2011-02-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

其中攝錄了指責西方國家外交政策錄像的7人辯稱他們只是打算製造一宗引人注目的政治事件，而無意殺害任何人。Ahmed Ali在法庭上宣稱他打算在希斯洛機場引爆一個小型裝置以驚嚇人們，而陰謀不涉及襲擊客機。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7564184.stm | work=BBC News | title=Liquid bomb plot: What happened | date=2008-09-09 | accessdate=2010-04-22 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wfdqKKJi?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/7564184.stm | archivedate=2011-02-21 | deadurl=no }}</ref>除了Mohammad Gulzar以外的所有被告承認策劃在公眾地方造成滋擾，Ali、Sarwar和Hussein也承認意圖引起爆炸。<ref name="BBC verdicts"/>

2008年11月8日，陪審團未有裁定任何被告意圖襲擊客機罪名成立。陪審團裁定Ali、Sarwar和Hussein陰謀進行謀殺罪名成立，但未能就陰謀炸毀客機的控罪達成裁決。<ref name="BBC verdicts">{{cite news | title = Airliners bomb plot: The Verdicts | publisher = BBC News | date = 2009-09-07 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8233954.stm | accessdate = 2009-09-07 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5whI4au0o?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8233954.stm | archivedate = 2011-02-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

2009年9月7日，另一個陪審團裁定Ahmed Abdulla Ali、Assad Sarwar和Tanvir Hussain「陰謀以液體炸彈進行謀殺」罪名成立。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8242238.stm |title='Three guilty of airline bomb plot' |date=2009-09-07 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2009-02-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5wfdnZy16?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8242238.stm |archivedate=2011-02-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>陪審團未能就Ibrahim Savant、Arafat Khan、Waheed Zaman和Unmar Islam的上述控罪達成裁決。Umar Islam的另一項陰謀進行謀殺控罪則成立。 <ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2009/sep/07/plane-bomb-plot-trial-verdicts |title='Three guilty of transatlantic bomb plot' |date=2009-09-07 |work=The Guardian |location=London |first=Vikram |last=Dodd |accessdate=2010-04-22 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5whI4nZaU?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2009/sep/07/plane-bomb-plot-trial-verdicts |archivedate=2011-02-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>Mohammad Gulzar的所有控罪被裁定不成立。<ref>{{cite news |date=2008-09-09 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7605583.stm |title='Astonishment' at terror verdicts |accessdate=2009-02-19 |publisher=BBC News |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5whI5iF6j?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/7605583.stm |archivedate=2011-02-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>法庭判決Sarwar需要至少服刑36年，Tanvir Hussain至少32年。<ref>{{cite news |date=2009-09-14 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8254156.stm |title='Airline plot trio get life terms' at terror verdicts |accessdate=2009-09-14 |publisher=BBC News |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5whI6H6Q5?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8254156.stm |archivedate=2011-02-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

2010年7月，Ibrahim Savant、Arafat Khan和Waheed Zaman在法庭被判決陰謀進行謀殺罪名成立，被判處終身監禁而需要服刑至少20年方可獲考慮假釋。<ref>{{cite news | title = Would-be suicide bombers jailed for life | date = 2010-07-12 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/10600084.stm | work = BBC News | accessdate = 2010-07-12 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5wfdoTJSe?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/10600084.stm | archivedate = 2011-02-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

